4ï¸âƒ£ serviceAccountToken
ğŸ‘‰ You can inject the token for the current service account into a Pod at a specified path.
ğŸ‘‰ Containers in this Pod can use that token to access the Kubernetes API server, authenticating with the identity of the pod's ServiceAccount.

âœ… A container using a projected volume source as a subPath volume mount will not receive updates for those volume sources.

